reviewText: I get so many compliments on a daily basis on these and they are still super comfortable even though they may not be AS comfortable as the originals.
No frills here. Just a basic tennis shoe. Fabric is what reebok has used for years. Comfortable and worth the money.

reviewerName: J. A. Black J.A. Black, English Major
reviewText: The Reebok Classics were so cute. I was delighted to find them for sale on Amazon. The width was perfect, but the length was a bit short for me, unfortunately.
summary: Reebok Women's Classic Nylon Sneaker--an old fav

reviewText: I like these shoes. They go great! My only problem is I have wide feet at the top. They cause no problem.I take a size 6 and they fit perfect and when I wear them I have no problems.
This was a second purchase of this product as my mother liked my sneaker so much she asked for this shoe for herself. Comfortable fit and great for walking.
Very comfortable.Classic.Good looking.Don't be jealous, just get your own pair. Seriously, get them.(Do yourself a favor and buy some shoe cleaner too...you are buying white shoes, afterall.)
